reviewText: Saw it at the theater and just had to have it for our collection. Great movie.

Why is 3D version not available direct from Amazon? Seems pretty stupid when Best Buy release sold out in less than a day, The demand is there, regardless of anti-3D propaganda. Problem with Disney? I see that Wonder Woman is available as pre-order Prime 3D set. Just strange...
Really good to watch and watch again.  I'm not sure what more could have been done for a first time title.
Can't play 3D on my system so it was a waste of money...might be able to use it as a doorstop tho...
This movie has it all. Comedy, romance, science fiction, and action.
I was pleasantly surprised.  This was an outstanding movie. Gunn knows EXACTLY how to make a superhero movie.  This hands down is my favorite Marvel movie.  3d is outstanding as well!
Good movie not good Price..best buy has it for 28$
